      "span_text": "While many scientiWc disciplines face huge diYculties when trying to experimentally validate theoretical predictions, protein modelling is in a fortunate situation: since 1994, the biennial Critical Assessment of Structure Prediction (CASP) contests  ) have provided an ideal opportunity to evaluate the accuracy of today's many protein structure prediction methods."
